howtoplay.rule=Rule
howtoplay.rule.title=How To Play > Rule
howtoplay.rule.header.1=Rule
howtoplay.rule.text.1=1.DO NOT harass, insult or troll users.
howtoplay.rule.text.2=2.DO NOT advertise other services or games.
howtoplay.rule.text.3=3.DO NOT use any skins and tools like modification, macro or scripting that give unfair advantages.
howtoplay.rule.text.4=4.DO NOT violate public order and morality.
howtoplay.rule.text.5=5.DO NOT share information for connecting server in public.
howtoplay.rule.text.6=6.DO NOT overload server.
howtoplay.rule.text.7=7.DO NOT abandon match intentionally.
howtoplay.rule.text.8=8.DO NOT multiple accounts to get exp or points abusively.
howtoplay.rule.text.9=9.DO NOT go to areas by using glitches where cannot be entered.
howtoplay.rule.text.10=10.DO NOT other behavior prohibited by administors.
howtoplay.rule.text.11=Player found breaking these rules can expect a warning or a suspension of access to the Splaturn Server and Discord. 
